---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <article>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
      #govbins is a project to photograph wheelie bins in every UK local
      council.
    </p>

    <p>
      Started in 2017, the catalogue is the work of dozens of people
      <a href="/submit-photos"> submitting photos </a> from across the UK and beyond.
    </p>
    <h2>Design and code</h2>
    <p>
      This website is made by friends
      <a href="https://www.harrytrimble.co.uk/">Harry Trimble</a> and
      <a href="http://tommyp.org/">Tommy Palmer</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="/build">How this site is built</a>.
    </p>
    <h2>Social media</h2>
    <p>
      Follow #govbins on{' '}
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/govbins.uk/">Instagram</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Press</h2>
    <p>
      <a
        href="https://www.theguardian.com/cities/2018/apr/02/the-beauty-of-bins-instagram-account-catalogues-cities-unique-designs"
      >
        The Guardian
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a
        href="https://www.creativereview.co.uk/bin-done-visual-catalogue-nations-bins/"
      >
        Creative Review
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a
        href="https://www.citylab.com/design/2018/03/britains-beautiful-garbage-bins/556217/"
      >
        Bloomberg
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a
        href="https://inews.co.uk/light-relief/offbeat/local-council-wheelie-bins/"
      >
        The Independent
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://qz.com/emails/quartz-obsession/1687384/"> Quartz </a> (scroll
      way down)
    </p>
    <p>
      <a
        href="https://www.gizmodo.co.uk/2020/08/this-website-shows-you-what-bins-look-like-around-the-uk/"
      >
        Gizmodo UK
      </a>
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.2rem 0;
    line-height: 2rem;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    line-height: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    article {
      margin-left: 10rem;
      width: 66.66%;
    }
  }
</style>
